'''''Shadowrealm''''' is the third and final novel in the [[The Twilight War]] trilogy by [[Paul S. Kemp]].

{{quote|''[[Erevis Cale|Cale]] inhaled deeply and fought back tears.''

''He allowed that on at least one night months ago the village owed its safety not to [[Yondalla]], but to him.  He had killed a score of [[troll]]s while he had answered to [[Jak Fleet|Jak]]'s ghost, while he tried to climb into the light.''

''But light was not for him. Not anymore.  Not ever.''
}}
